<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Admin: Add City | CineReserve</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            mint: {
              50: '#f0fdf4',
              100: '#dcfce7',
              200: '#bbf7d0',
              500: '#10b981',
              600: '#059669',
              900: '#064e3b',
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>

<body class="bg-mint-50 text-mint-900 min-h-screen font-sans selection:bg-mint-200">

  <nav class="p-6 bg-white border-b border-mint-100 flex justify-between items-center sticky top-0 z-50 shadow-sm">
    <div class="max-w-5xl w-full mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
      <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-black text-mint-900 tracking-tighter flex items-center gap-2">
        CineReserve üé¨ 
        <span class="text-[10px] uppercase bg-mint-900 text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-md tracking-widest ml-2">Admin</span>
      </a>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
        <a href="/admin" class="text-sm font-bold text-mint-600 hover:text-mint-900 transition-colors">Dashboard</a>
        <a href="/" class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 hover:text-mint-900 transition-colors">‚Üê Exit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="max-w-xl mx-auto py-16 px-6">
    
    <div class="mb-10 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-mint-900 mb-2">Expansion</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium">Add a new geographical hub to the network</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] border border-mint-100 shadow-2xl shadow-mint-200/40 p-10 mb-10 transition-all hover:shadow-mint-200/60">
      <form action="/api/cities" method="POST" class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <label for="name" class="block text-xs font-black uppercase text-mint-900/40 mb-3 ml-1 tracking-widest">
            Official City Name
          </label>
          <input 
            type="text" 
            id="name"
            name="name" 
            placeholder="e.g. San Francisco" 
            required
            class="w-full bg-mint-50 border border-mint-100 rounded-2xl p-5 text-mint-900 font-bold focus:ring-4 focus:ring-mint-200 focus:border-mint-500 outline-none transition-all placeholder:text-mint-200 text-lg"
          >
        </div>

        <button 
          type="submit" 
          class="w-full bg-mint-900 text-white text-lg font-black py-5 rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-mint-900/20 hover:bg-black transition-all transform active:scale-[0.98] flex items-center justify-center gap-3"
        >
          <span>Confirm & Add City</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
          </svg>
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white border border-mint-200 rounded-3xl p-6 flex gap-4 items-center shadow-sm">
      <div class="bg-mint-100 p-3 rounded-2xl">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-mint-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-mint-900/70 leading-relaxed font-medium">
        Newly added cities will immediately appear in the <span class="text-mint-600 font-bold">Public Hub</span> and the <span class="text-mint-600 font-bold">Show Scheduler</span>.
      </p>
    </div>

  </main>

  <footer class="py-10 text-center text-mint-200 text-[10px] uppercase font-black tracking-[0.2em]">
    CineReserve Administrative Portal &bull; Internal Use Only &bull; 2026
  </footer>

</body>
</html>